songs.title: Text You Pictures
songs.lyrics:
I just can't wait to feel you
Vibrate on my phone and think of you
I'll text you pictures
Right on my phone-phone
All the time
Right on my phone

Baby you know, know
You left a mark, mark
Do you remember when we
Taped it in the dark, dark?
I talk for free, free
And honestly-ly
Do you remember when we
Taped it in the dark-dark?
Sometimes I see, see
You’re wanting me, me
But baby I don’t care
I’ll text you one for free, free
